    This parser was created especially for RapidWright. It is only intended to read EDIF generated from Xilinx Vivado. It is not intended to be a fully general purpose EDIF parser. If you have EDIF that you want to read into RapidWright, load it into Vivado first and then write it out from Vivado. Created on: May 10, 2017
